	   <tr><td colspan=2>I just made a Bard...I want to buy her some armor...I have about 1500pp to spend. What are the important stats for a Bard?&nbsp;&nbsp;Dex, Sta, &amp; Str?  Thank you =)<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Dec 17 22:16:05 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Madelyna</td></tr>
