	   <tr><td colspan=2>This question probably has come up in the past, but since I don't see it the recent posts. I figure I will ask the question again and raise some discussion.<br><br>Why is it that we (Bards) receive the skill brass instruments at Level 11 and we don't receive our first brass instrument song until level 18 and at the same time have to wait until level 14 to get wind instruments when we have a wind instrument song at level 11?<br><br>This doesn't make sense. I think the 2 skills should be reversed. Why should I waste skill points at level 11 when I can't use the skill until level 18.<br><br>Your thoughts?<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
